M|Comm|tx|3. RECOMMENDATION   — Full cg st (Pass 3 output only)
M|Comm|tx|4. tst ds      — 2+ variants named, hypothesis stated, sc metric and timeline defined
M|Comm|tx|5. kh FLAG    — Gate cleared or specific issue flagged and resolved
M|Comm|tx|```
